  <Summary>Razor is on the hunt for a 12 year old girl abducted and missing for two days. She tracks her down to a building where she bursts in and dispatches every man inside with brutal ease. She even takes the head of the main man right in front of the girl after she has already brought him to his knees.

 

She drops the girl off with the police before following a lead on trafficing from the raid killing all but one inside the warehouse. She leaves him to get a message to his boss about who did this. the man delivers the message and gets his face shredded by Von Drake who contacts Stryke and gives her orders to go after Razor.

Razor #0 Souls of Darkness was originally released in 1991 at SDCC as a signed preview edition limited to 300 copies. This is the first comic book published featuring Razor. It was later republished in 1995 as the "London Knight Edition"</Summary>
